If you are in the US, try Disneyland in California or Disney World Orlando vacation packages if your destination is Florida.

Disneyland Paris is a must for children and entertains all ages.

Disneyland Paris tickets cost 61 euro / day per adult and 55 euro / day for children aged 3 to 11.

