Attractions include opening day's Jungle Cruise , the "Temple of the Forbidden Eye" in Indiana Jones Adventure , and Tarzan's Treehouse , which is a conversion of the earlier Swiss Family Robinson Tree House from the Walt Disney film, Swiss Family Robinson .

Walt Disney's Enchanted Tiki Room which is located at the entrance to Adventureland is the first feature attraction to employ Audio-Animatronics , a computer synchronization of sound and robotics.

Disney California Adventure Park was added in what used to be a parking lot for Disneyland guests.

