It's A Small World is a classic Disney attraction that is a boat ride taking guests around the world.

Each part of the world has dolls that sing the song "It's a Small World" in their language.

Pinocchio's Daring Journey is another ride that allows riders to explore the story of the Pinocchio Disney movie.

Guests can see different small villages of classic Disney stories on the Storybook Land Canal Boats.

One of Disneyland's first attractions can be ridden here.

Tarzan's Treehouse was originally named The Swiss Family Treehouse after an old novel.

The Indiana Jones Adventure is a ride in a jeep through "dangerous" caverns that include lava, a giant snake, and other perils.

Disneyland's newest attraction can be found here.

It is called " Buzz Lightyear Astro Blasters" and it opened in 2005 .

